{"id":316398,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/10/维权网-王荔蕻等人祝福刘贤斌生日（图）/","date":"2013-10-03T15:35:19Z","modified":"2013-10-03T15:35:19Z","title":"维权网 | 王荔蕻等人祝福刘贤斌生日（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员一文报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日是刘贤斌</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">45</span><span>岁生日，下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>点，王荔蕻、胡佳、莫之许、刘强本、阿尔、殷龙龙、冯传林、高健等人，在北京的一家酒店为刘贤斌庆生，巧克力色的蛋糕上贴着“自由贤斌”的字样，由刘贤斌的四川老乡莫之许点燃蜡烛，大家一起唱起了生日歌，同时打出“自由无价、贤斌生快”的字样，来寄托大家对刘贤斌的思念之情。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>联想到认识刘贤斌的情景，人权捍卫者王荔蕻说，“第一次见到他是在北京的一个大排档吃饭，谁能想到一个刚坐了十年牢的人能那么乐观，后来我在监狱有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">81</span><span>天没有放风的时候，唯一想到的精神支柱就是刘贤斌”！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>高健回忆说，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>年“陈扬关注团”路过成都出火车站时，外面下着雨，而刘贤斌一直打着伞站在那里等着我们，那种平易近人的态度一直感动着我。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>       </span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>年北京公民为刘贤斌过生日的时候，三位诗人殷龙龙、阿尔、刘强本每人写了一首诗，这次大家再次念涌起那份诗歌中隐含的思念。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-VjHaIrj1b7o/Uk2JeB8RxgI/AAAAAAAApAM/kT89ZKbAKuE/s1600/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE00.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"237\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-VjHaIrj1b7o/Uk2JeB8RxgI/AAAAAAAApAM/kT89ZKbAKuE/s320/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE00.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>附诗歌四篇</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>附：</span><span>殷龙龙诗<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>异见</span><span>――</span><span>为刘贤斌的生日聚会匆忙而作<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>我们都应该过生日<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>哪怕是在牢里，哪怕是与祖国同庆<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>日子越过越多，多得好像犯人<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>日子红红火火，烧起来可以清理污浊的山河<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>我们点上蜡烛<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>埋下一个恒古的心愿<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>裤脚溅上泥巴<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>袖口灌满了秋风<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>把十月装进烟盒；喷云吐雾的日子<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>和我们成了莫逆之交<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>我们长高一厘米返老还童<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>我们吹出莫须有的罪名天高地厚<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>我们生为了我们日<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>我们掐灭一支烟，为了怀孕，孕住火种——新中国<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>阿尔诗：<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>给刘贤斌兄弟<span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>其实，真正的兄弟<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>只需要一个滚烫的眼神<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>一句“我们在一起”的简单话语<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>一双粗糙大手的紧紧一握<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>刘贤斌<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>我们认识你<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>只是在废都五月的一天<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>你与屠夫等人<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>在街头大排档喝酒<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>一声从从容容的王大姐、一声从从容容的阿尔兄<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>就消融了所有的陌生与距离<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>短短<span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span>分钟，我们就成了血脉相连的兄弟<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>可万万没有想到<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>你又被关进了牢房，而新的构陷<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>竟在上次出狱的那一天<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>就开始了<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>巴蜀的酷吏，没人性到了丧心病狂<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>此刻，我们满腔悲愤<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>但不再哀伤……我们要没日没夜地集结正义的声音<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>撕心裂魄的无罪呐喊将是大家无尽的秋风、秋雨与秋雷——震塌那邪恶的墙<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>让盆地沐浴高原的朗朗阳光<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>阳光下兄弟们大碗的烧酒、砰砰地撞响<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>七律·给刘贤斌兄弟<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>西蜀皂隶滥捕人，四海惊呼刘贤斌<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>君求公正行大义，魔施巫术起贼心<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>三度楚囚强项令，二世荆冠草根魂<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>夜梦兄弟共把酒，乍醒恸痛泪沾襟<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>刘强本诗：<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>獄</span><span>の中</span><span>國――</span><span>兼致</span><span>劉賢</span><span>斌先生<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>十月已至<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>秋</span><span>風</span><span>穿在身上<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>多少有些寒意<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>脫</span><span>不下</span><span>來</span><span>的<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>還</span><span>有</span><span>幾</span><span>千年的沉屙<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>和遍地的冤魂<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>一</span><span>個</span><span>下跪的民族<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>正在成</span><span>為</span><span>世界的</span><span>負</span><span>荷<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>十月已至<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>落</span><span>葉繽紛</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>紛紛</span><span>失去自己的名字<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>自己的血性<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>在</span><span>獄</span><span>之</span><span>國</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>是</span><span>誰</span><span>把我</span><span>們</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>手</span><span>槍</span><span>一</span><span>樣</span><span>拆</span><span>來</span><span>拆去<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>連</span><span>同我</span><span>們</span><span>的屈辱和土地<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>十月已至<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>晴朗的天空<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>多</span><span>麼適</span><span>合</span><span>寫</span><span>下<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>藍</span><span>草莓的</span><span>詩</span><span>句<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>我想</span><span>寫</span><span>一首</span><span>歡樂</span><span>的</span><span>詩</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>寫</span><span>出</span><span>個</span><span>一位仁者</span><span>溫</span><span>厚的胸襟<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>他</span><span>讓</span><span>十三</span><span>億</span><span>中</span><span>國</span><span>人<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>不再以十三</span><span>億獄</span><span>友相</span><span>稱</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010.10.2</span><span>黃</span><span>昏于南磨房<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}